[
  {
    "content_id": 619300,
    "reference_id": 8976,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:1",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001001",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>提摩太是保羅最親密的同工之一，他們的關係非常緊密。提摩太的工作非常重要，以至於保羅將他也列為這封信的發信人。保羅也在哥林多後書、腓立比書、帖撒羅尼迦前後書以及腓利門書中提到過他。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001001",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:1",
          "end_ref": "51001001",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:1"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619309,
    "reference_id": 8985,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:2",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001002",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>歌羅西位於小亞細亞西部的呂卡河（Lycus River）河谷中。它位於以弗所東方約 193 公里（120 英里），以及老底嘉東南方約 16 公里（10 英里）。它位於一條重要的羅馬道路上，因此受到當時社會和宗教潮流的影響。</p></li><li><p><em>弟兄</em>：希臘文 <em>adelphoi</em>，這個詞是用來指家庭成員，包括男性和女性。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001002",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:2",
          "end_ref": "51001002",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:2"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619310,
    "reference_id": 8986,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:3–14",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001003-51001014",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>這段經文以感謝開始，這在新約聖經的書信中很常見。保羅感謝神讓歌羅西信徒的信心增長。他祈禱他們對信仰能有更深的認識。透過這個禱告，保羅表達了他對假教師的影響的關切。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001003",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:3",
          "end_ref": "51001014",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:14"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619311,
    "reference_id": 8987,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:4",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001004",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p><em>眾聖徒</em>（意指<em>聖潔的人</em>）：新約聖經稱所有基督徒為<em>聖徒</em>。他們被神分別出來作為祂聖潔的子民（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:12\">3:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001004",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:4",
          "end_ref": "51001004",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:4"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619312,
    "reference_id": 8988,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:5",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>歌羅西的基督徒所擁有的堅定盼望，為他們的信心和愛心提供了穩固的根基（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:4\">1:4</a>）。</p><ul><li><p>神為信徒所預備的事物尚未完全彰顯，但它已經存在於天（天堂）上。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001005",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:5",
          "end_ref": "51001005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:5"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619313,
    "reference_id": 8989,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:6",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001006",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>透過改變生命在各處結出果子：這好消息能有效地改變生命並帶來屬靈的成長（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:10\">1:10</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001006",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:6",
          "end_ref": "51001006",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:6"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619314,
    "reference_id": 8990,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:7",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001007",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>以巴弗（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12-Col4:13\">4:12–13</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:23\">門1:23</a>）可能是在保羅在以弗所服事時歸信的（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts19:10\">徒19:10</a>），然後他返回歌羅西，將好消息帶回到他自己的家鄉。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001007",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:7",
          "end_ref": "51001007",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:7"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619315,
    "reference_id": 8991,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:9–10",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001009-51001010",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅祈求神讓他的讀者能夠更深刻地理解福音，並能在他們的生活中將其充分展現出來。屬靈的成長會帶來對基督真理更清晰和更深入的理解，以及活出蒙神喜悅的行為。藉此，信徒就會有堅忍和耐心能在邪惡面前站立得穩（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:11\">1:11</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001009",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:9",
          "end_ref": "51001010",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:10"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619294,
    "reference_id": 8970,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:12–13",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001012-51001013",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>總是感謝父：謙卑地感謝神的救恩是抵抗錯誤教導的引誘的有力對策（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:7\">2:7</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:17\">3:17</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:2\">4:2</a>）。</p></li><li><p>基業是神所應許給祂子民的（例如，見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut3:28\">申3:28</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:12\">詩33:12</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek44:28\">結44:28</a>）。在新約聖經中，<em>基業</em>包含了救恩和最終的拯救（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:11\">弗1:11</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:7\">多3:7</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:15\">來9:15</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001012",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:12",
          "end_ref": "51001013",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:13"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619296,
    "reference_id": 8972,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:15",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001015",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>可見的形像：在舊約聖經的希臘文翻譯中，eikōn（「形像，代表」）是用來指人類是按照神的形像被造的（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:26-Gen1:27\">創1:26–27</a>），也用來指在猶太文獻中的智慧形像（見<em>所羅門智訓</em> 7:25–26）。新約聖經的作者談到基督是神的智慧，藉此來闡明祂的重要性（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:24\">林前1:24</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">30</a>）。</p></li><li><p>祂在一切被造之前就已存在，並且在所有受造物之上是至高無上的（或<em>祂是在一切被造的以先</em>）：這個片語在早期基督徒關於基督本質的辯論中佔有重要地位。<em>長子</em>（和合本譯：被造的以先）並不意味著祂是被創造出來的；這是一個從舊約聖經中所得出的稱謂，表示其地位上的至高無上和時序上的優先性（見，例如，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:27\">詩89:27</a>）。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:15",
          "end_ref": "51001015",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:15"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619295,
    "reference_id": 8971,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:15–20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001015-51001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅將耶穌表達為至高無上的創造者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:17\">1:15–17</a>）和救贖者（<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:18-Col1:20\">1:18–20</a>）。這一系列簡短的陳述、對基督崇高的觀念，以及語言和思想上的平行結構，都強烈暗示這些經文引用了一首早期基督教關於耶穌的讚美詩，而保羅就將這讚美詩應用於歌羅西信徒的處境。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001015",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:15",
          "end_ref": "51001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619297,
    "reference_id": 8973,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:16",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001016",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>有位的、主治的、執政的與掌權的，指的是無形世界中的屬靈權勢。這句話強調了基督的至高超越了那些受到假教師極力關注的權勢（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:18\">2:18</a>）。</p></li><li><p>萬物都是藉著祂並為祂而創造的：基督既是創造萬物的憑藉，也是所有創造的目標。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001016",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:16",
          "end_ref": "51001016",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:16"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619298,
    "reference_id": 8974,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:18",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001018",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<ul><li><p>教會的頭（和合本譯為：教會……之首）：希臘詞 kephalē（頭）通常是保羅用於表達<em>權柄</em>或<em>首領</em>的隱喻（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:10\">2:10</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">19</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:3-1Cor11:10\">林前11:3–10</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:15\">弗4:15</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23\">5:23</a>）。</p></li><li><p>這是祂的身體：教會作為基督身體的隱喻表達了基督與教會本質上的合一（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:24\">西1:24</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:19\">2:19</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:15\">3:15</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:23\">弗1:23</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:16\">2:16</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:4\">4:4</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:12\">12</a>，<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:23\">5:23</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:30\">30</a>）。</p></li><li><p>超越所有從死裡復活的人（或<em>從死裏首先復生的</em>）：見<span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"8972\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">研讀註釋西1:15</span>。</p></li></ul>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001018",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:18",
          "end_ref": "51001018",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:18"
        }
      ],
      "resource": [
        {
          "reference_id": 8972,
          "content_id": 619296,
          "resource_code": "TyndaleStudyNotes",
          "label": "歌羅西書 1:15",
          "language": "zht"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619299,
    "reference_id": 8975,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:19",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001019",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>神在祂一切的豐盛中強調了祂已選擇在耶穌基督裡完全地啟示自己。因此，看見耶穌、認識耶穌也就是看見並認識神（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6-John14:11\">約14:6–11</a>）。假教師似乎主張基督徒需要尋求其它靈體（靈性的存在）來了解更多關於神的事（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:16\">西1:16</a>、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:20\">20</a>）。然而，基督已足以讓我們認識神的一切（參<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8-Col2:9\">2:8–9</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001019",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:19",
          "end_ref": "51001019",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:19"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619301,
    "reference_id": 8977,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:20",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001020",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>藉著基督，神使萬有與自己和好，重新建立了祂對一切創造之物的統治，包括屬靈和屬世的領域。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001020",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:20",
          "end_ref": "51001020",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:20"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619303,
    "reference_id": 8979,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:21",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001021",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>從前與神隔絕這個片語指的可能是他們作為外邦人的狀態（見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:12\">弗2:12</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:21",
          "end_ref": "51001021",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:21"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619302,
    "reference_id": 8978,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:21–23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001021-51001023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅將<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:20\">一章15至20節</a>的真理應用於歌羅西的基督徒。作為已經與神和好的子民，他們享有新的屬靈身份，並需要堅定持守所領受的真理。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001021",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:21",
          "end_ref": "51001023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619304,
    "reference_id": 8980,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:22",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001022",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>歌羅西信徒就和所有信徒一樣，在神的眼中是聖潔且無可指責的，這並不是因為他們自身的完美，而是因為他們藉著基督的死與神和好。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001022",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:22",
          "end_ref": "51001022",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:22"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619305,
    "reference_id": 8981,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:23",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001023",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>傳與普天下萬人（字面意思是<em>向天下萬物傳講</em>）：保羅使用誇張法<span>（為了強調而誇大）的重點，是要</span>表明傳揚福音的中心已經在羅馬世界的重要城市中被建立起來（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:6\">1:6</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001023",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:23",
          "end_ref": "51001023",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:23"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619307,
    "reference_id": 8983,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:24",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001024",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>我參與在基督的苦難中（和合本譯為：在我肉身上補滿基督患難的缺欠）：雖然基督救贖的苦難是獨特的且已全然成就，但基督仍然透過祂的子民在一個對救贖信息充滿敵意的世界中繼續受苦。基督和祂的教會將會繼續受苦，直到神在這個世上的旨意成全（另見<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:19-Mark13:23\">可13:19–23</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:17-Rom8:18\">羅8:17–18</a>；<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess3:3\">帖前3:3</a>）。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:24",
          "end_ref": "51001024",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 1:24"
        }
      ],
      "resource": []
    }
  },
  {
    "content_id": 619306,
    "reference_id": 8982,
    "title": "歌羅西書 1:24–25",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "51001024-51002005",
    "language": "zht",
    "content": "<p>保羅看待自己在好消息廣傳中的職分(<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:23\">1:23</a>)。</p>",
    "associations": {
      "passage": [
        {
          "start_ref": "51001024",
          "start_ref_usfm": "COL 1:24",
          "end_ref": "51002005",
          "end_ref_usfm": "COL 2:5"
        }
